item.title: Fail Compilation March 2011 || TNL
item.description:
Fail Compilation March 2011 || TNL
The fail compilation of March is online. The best fails this month in one single video. I hope you all enjoy it. It really took some time to find the best videos around the net from the last month. The last 30 seconds has fails from previous months. Just because I wanted to show you some older fails which deserve some attention. I hope to see you this Sunday for the next mini compilation. I will try to upload 1 compilation per week. I would also like to thank you all for the February compilation. If you all wouldn't helped me this wasn't possible. Thank you :) I also resolved the copyright issues I had with youtube. This account doesn't run a chance of getting removed. This month it will be 2 years ago when I uploaded the first fail compilation. I tried to improve the fail compilation every video. Some of the best improvements I made. No music. Changed from numbers to months (fail compilation march 2011 instead of fail compilation nr. 21) No logo's from websites (break.com etc.). On some points I was the first and now everyone followed me. Although no one ever managed to duplicate me, only imitations have been made. I will continue to be the leading compilation maker. Also, if you want to help me with this video you can help me the following ways. I will thank you a lot for it. - Rate/favorite/comment - Share on facebook and other websites you know. - Subscribe (only if you're really interested in all the videos I upload, I won't do sub4sub and stuff) I'm always searching for good fails. If you've found a good fail or win video, just send me a Private Message (PM). I will always watch your submissions and if I like it, I'll add it into one of the compilations. Also, if you want to follow me, you can do it on the following places. You will get background information about stuff I do and stuff. Twitter (English & Dutch): http://twitter.com/twisterholland I have a new blog: http://twisternederland.blogspot.com (haven't updated for a while, I'll start within a few days).
